 \tgolang.org/x/text v0.32.0 // indirect\n71: \tgolang.org/x/time v0.3.0 // indirect\n72: \tgoogle.golang.org/protobuf v1.34.2 // indirect\n73: \tgopkg.in/evanphx/json-patch.v4 v4.12.0 // indirect\n74: \tgopkg.in/inf.v0 v0.9.1 // indirect\n75: \tgopkg.in/yaml.v2 v2.4.0 // indirect\n76: \tgopkg.in/yaml.v3 v3.0.1 // indirect\n77: \tk8s.io/kube-openapi v0.0.0-20240228011516-70dd3763d340 // indirect\n78: \tsigs.k8s.io/json v0.0.0-20221116044647-bc3834ca7abd // indirect\n79: \tsigs.k8s.io/structured-merge-diff/v4 v4.4.1 // indirect\n80: \tsigs.k8s.io/yaml v1.4.0 // indirect\n81: )\n\n(End of file - total 81 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"module github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube\n\ngo 1.25.7\n\nrequire (\n\tgithub.com/alicebob/miniredis/v2 v2.37.0\n\tgithub.com/gin-gonic/gin v1.10.0\n\tgithub.com/go-chi/chi/v5 v5.0.12\n\tgithub.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5 v5.2.1\n\tgithub.com/redis/go-redis/v9 v9.18.0\n\tgithub.com/stretchr/testify v1.9.0\n\tgolang.org/x/net v0.48.0\n\tk8s.io/api v0.31.0\n\tk8s.io/apimachinery v0.31.0\n\tk8s.io/client-go v0.31.0\n\tk8s.io/klog/v2 v2.130.1\n\tk8s.io/utils v0.0.0-20240711033017-18e509b52bc8\n\tsigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime v0.19.0\n)\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/go.mod","time":{"start":1775860893699,"end":1775860893715}}}}
