riteria\n379: \n380: - [ ] All 8 source files created in `pkg/picod/`\n381: - [ ] Entry point `cmd/picod/main.go` created\n382: - [ ] Config struct with Port and Workspace fields\n383: - [ ] Server struct with Gin engine, AuthManager, workspace, startTime\n384: - [ ] JWT RS256 authentication with 5 error cases\n385: - [ ] Execute handler with timeout, working_dir, env support\n386: - [ ] File upload handler supporting multipart and JSON/Base64\n387: - [ ] File list and download handlers with path sanitization\n388: - [ ] Health check handler (no auth required)\n389: - [ ] sanitizePath with workspace jail enforcement\n390: - [ ] Pass `go vet`\n391: - [ ] Pass `golangci-lint`\n392: - [ ] Test coverage ≥ 80%\n393: - [ ] Binary runs with JWT auth and executes commands\n394: \n395: ---\n396: \n397: ## File Changes Summary\n398: \n399: | File | Action | Lines Changed |\n400: |------|--------|---------------|\n401: | `go.mod` | Modify | +2 (gin, jwt dependencies) |\n402: | `pkg/picod/config.go` | Create | ~15 lines |\n403: | `pkg/picod/server.go` | Create | ~80 lines |\n404: | `pkg/picod/auth.go` | Create | ~100 lines |\n405: | `pkg/picod/execute.go` | Create | ~100 lines |\n406: | `pkg/picod/files.go` | Create | ~150 lines |\n407: | `pkg/picod/health.go` | Create | ~20 lines |\n408: | `pkg/picod/sanitize.go` | Create | ~50 lines |\n409: | `cmd/picod/main.go` | Create | ~40 lines |\n410: | `pkg/picod/picod_test.go` | Create | ~200 lines |\n411: \n412: ---\n413: \n414: ## Implementation Notes\n415: \n416: - Gin framework: `gin.New()` for engine, `gin.SetMode(gin.ReleaseMode)` for production\n417: - JWT validation: use `jwt.WithExpirationRequired()`, `jwt.WithLeeway(time.Minute)`\n418: - RSA signing: type-assert `token.Method` to `*jwt.SigningMethodRSA`\n419: - Path sanitization: `filepath.EvalSymlinks()` for symlink resolution, `filepath.Rel()` for traversal check\n420: - Command execution: `exec.CommandContext()` for timeout enforcement, exit code 124 for timeout\n421: - Base64 decoding: `base64.StdEncoding.DecodeString()` for JSON file upload\n422: - File mode parsing: `strconv.ParseUint(modeStr, 8, 32)` for octal parsing\n\n(End of file - total 422 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-015 — PicoD 命令执行 API Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-015 — PicoD 命令执行 API |\n| Module | `pkg/picod` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Dependencies Setup\n\n- [ ] **T1.1** Add gin dependency\n  - Run: `go get github.com/gin-gonic/gin@v1.10.0`","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-015/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775860893697,"end":1775860893726}}}}
